    "It can \"scaffold\" users through their tasks by suggesting actionable tips, outlining the next steps, and recommending best practices.",
    "GenAI has the ability to \"remember\" the context and history of conversations with users.",
    "This enables it to deliver personalized responses and examples, which further enhance the learning experience and facilitate the retention of new knowledge.",
    "Organizations such as Khan Academy and DuoLingo have already integrated these and other GenAI functionalities into their learning support systems.",
    "Within organizational settings, users can learn on the job through interactions with GenAI."
